"{\n \"heroStructure\": [\n  {\n   \"tag\": \"h1\",\n   \"cls\": \"h1 l:w-auto w-max\",\n   \"text\": \"we create feelings.\",\n   \"src\": \"\"\n  },\n  {\n   \"tag\": \"h2\",\n   \"cls\": \"h2 section-title text-right\",\n   \"text\": \"Great design doesn’t just guide behavior.\",\n   \"src\": \"\"\n  },\n  {\n   \"tag\": \"h2\",\n   \"cls\": \"h2 section-title\",\n   \"text\": \"It speaks directly to the nervous system.\",\n   \"src\": \"\"\n  }\n ],\n \"s2marqueeRows\": [],\n \"s2awards\": [\n  {\n   \"cls\": \"flex flex-col\",\n   \"text\": \"26 (including) FWA OF THE YEAR FWA ANNUAL PEOPLE’S CHOICE\"\n  },\n  {\n   \"cls\": \"flex flex-col\",\n   \"text\": \"11\"\n  },\n  {\n   \"cls\": \"flex flex-col\",\n   \"text\": \"11\"\n  },\n  {\n   \"cls\": \"flex flex-col\",\n   \"text\": \"10 (including) CSSDA SITE OF THE DAY CSSDA SITE OF THE MONTH\"\n  },\n  {\n   \"cls\": \"flex flex-col\",\n   \"text\": \"6\"\n  },\n  {\n   \"cls\": \"flex flex-col\",\n   \"text\": \"1\"\n  }\n ],\n \"s2fullText\": \"we stimulate memory. We’ve created experiences for the world’s most impactful brands. The industry has taken note. 26 (including) FWA OF THE YEAR FWA ANNUAL PEOPLE’S CHOICE 11 11 10 (including) CSSDA SITE OF THE DAY CSSDA SITE OF THE MONTH 6 1\",\n \"s3items\": [\n  {\n   \"title\": \"\",\n   \"body\": \"\",\n   \"cls\": \"services_item w-full flex flex-row items-end min-h-160 px-20 gap-10 py-13 bg-white s:min-h-80 s:px-cont s:py-10\"\n  },\n  {\n   \"title\": \"Architecture\",\n   \"body\": \"We build to inspire, but also build to code. At Mantis, design is only as strong as its function. Our architects specialize in bridging imagination with reality, ensuring bold concepts meet practical standards. Our network of fabricators span globally and across specialities; whether you’re creating small scale builds, large permanent structures, or sculpted art pieces - we’ve got you covered. RELATED SERVICES Creative and Design DirectionMoodboardsStage DesignRetail DesignFloorplansStructural DesignCAD RendersHigh Res 3D MocksFabrication PlansPermitting & Compliance Consulting Reach out for examples! Copied! hey@mantis.works hey@mantis.works\",\n   \"cls\": \"services_item white-gradient-light flex flex-col backdrop-blur-2xl accordion w-full\"\n  },\n  {\n   \"title\": \"Spatial & Interior Design\",\n   \"body\": \"A well-designed space balances openness and intimacy to draw people in and keep them engaged. We design with flow, psychology, and resonance in mind, creating environments that invite exploration and spark conversation long after the visit. RELATED SERVICES Creative and Design DirectionMoodboardsRetailWayfinding and Signage SystemsAR/VR/XR Integration in Physical SpacesEnvironmental DesignSpatial PlanningLighting PlanningMaterial Curation and SourcingFurniture and Decor Curation and SourcingHigh Res 3D Mocks Reach out for examples! Copied! hey@mantis.works hey@mantis.works\",\n   \"cls\": \"services_item white-gradient-light flex flex-col backdrop-blur-2xl accordion w-full\"\n  },\n  {\n   \"title\": \"Interactive / Creative Technology\",\n   \"body\": \"Experiences that anticipate what users want and need, paired with intuitive interfaces that support those actions, are our bread and butter. Our network of technologists—equal parts developer and artist—ensures every layer feels purposeful and magical. From reactive environments to projection-mapped performances, we design technology that transforms ideas into “wow” moments. RELATED SERVICES Creative and Design DirectionInteractive PrototypingGenerative ContentStage DesignGame DesignAI Model TrainingProjection MappingReactive EnvironmentsLight ProgrammingSoundscapes & Immersive AudioR&D / Labs Reach out for examples! Copied! hey@mantis.works hey@mantis.works\",\n   \"cls\": \"services_item white-gradient-light flex flex-col backdrop-blur-2xl accordion w-full\"\n  },\n  {\n   \"title\": \"Event Production\",\n   \"body\": \"We always deliver a smooth on-site experience by clearly defining roles & responsibilities, communication plans, escalation paths, detailed run of shows, and call sheets. Ahead of being on-site, we run through a detailed production book – culminating all the project details to use as the source of truth for all teams. RELATED SERVICES Fabrication ManagementStaffing ManagementLogistics / Tour ManagementProduction BooksRun-of-ShowsCall SheetsPermittingBrand Ambassador TrainingF&B ManagementDJ / Talent ManagementInsurance Coordination Reach out for examples! Copied! hey@mantis.works hey@mantis.works\",\n   \"cls\": \"services_item white-gradient-light flex flex-col backdrop-blur-2xl accordion w-full\"\n  },\n  {\n   \"title\": \"\",\n   \"body\": \"\",\n   \"cls\": \"services_item w-full flex flex-row items-end min-h-160 px-20 gap-10 py-13 bg-white s:min-h-80 s:px-cont s:py-10\"\n  },\n  {\n   \"title\": \"3D Modelling\",\n   \"body\": \"We deliver full-service 3D pipelines tailored to your project. From avatar systems to real-time content for live shows, we build assets designed to impress. Every piece is optimized across platforms so visuals don’t just look great, they perform flawlessly. RELATED SERVICES Creative and Design DirectionCharacter DesignEnvironment DesignModellingRiggingTexturingOptimization3D Fashion Reach out for examples! Copied! hey@mantis.works hey@mantis.works\",\n   \"cls\": \"services_item white-gradient-light flex flex-col backdrop-blur-2xl accordion w-full\"\n  },\n  {\n   \"title\": \"Motion & Animation\",\n   \"body\": \"Strong storytelling drives our work. We collaborate with world-class motion artists who understand movement as one of the most powerful communication tools. Whether constructing entire worlds or animating static designs, motion and animation are central to Mantis. RELATED SERVICES Creative and Design DirectionStoryboardingAnimaticsMotion GuidelinesInteractive WalkthroughsContent AnimationWeb Animation3D Animation Reach out for examples! Copied! hey@mantis.works hey@mantis.works\",\n   \"cls\": \"services_item white-gradient-light flex flex-col backdrop-blur-2xl accordion w-full\"\n  },\n  {\n   \"title\": \"User Experience / Interface\",\n   \"body\": \"We don’t rely on best practices. Each project begins from scratch to create systems that are genuinely bespoke. When we reference the past, we evolve it into something uniquely yours. Experience is at the core of our approach. Systems of any scale need architects who anticipate behavior before it happens. For over twenty years, we’ve been shaping pioneering interfaces for the web, and we continue to apply this thinking to current and emerging platforms. RELATED SERVICES Creative and Design DirectionWireframingPrototypingInsightsWeb DesignApp DesignProduct DesignDesign SystemsPlatform DesignVR/XR/ARFilter Design and ImplementationGraphic Design Reach out for examples! Copied! hey@mantis.works\",\n   \"cls\": \"services_item white-gradient-light flex flex-col backdrop-blur-2xl accordion w-full\"\n  },\n  {\n   \"title\": \"Development\",\n   \"body\": \"A digital experience is only as good as it functions. We work with the best technologists early and often in our process to plan and build performant tested experiences. Development makes our work better, and is a critical collaborator in our process at Mantis. RELATED SERVICES Technical DirectionFront-End DevelopmentWebGLCMS IntegrationE-Commerce IntegrationQADeploymentSystems IntegrationPerformance Analytics / Data VisualizationR&D/Labs Reach out for examples! Copied! hey@mantis.works hey@mantis.works\",\n   \"cls\": \"services_item white-gradient-light flex flex-col backdrop-blur-2xl accordion w-full\"\n  },\n  {\n   \"title\": \"\",\n   \"body\": \"\",\n   \"cls\": \"services_item w-full flex flex-row items-end min-h-160 px-20 gap-10 py-13 bg-white s:min-h-80 s:px-cont s:py-10\"\n  },\n  {\n   \"title\": \"Brand & Campaign Strategy\",\n   \"body\": \"Great ideas need direction. We offer scalable strategies—sometimes instinct-driven, sometimes data-backed—that gives your project a clear foundation. We design campaigns around the moments that matter, turning strategy into executions that catch the eye and spark engagement. Campaigns can focus on a single channel or expand into 360º ecosystems—experiential, digital, and content working together. RELATED SERVICES Strategic and Creative DirectionConsumer/Audience InsightsAudience DefinitionBrand PositioningIdeationStrategic ConsultingCopywriting & Messaging Reach out for examples! Copied! hey@mantis.works hey@mantis.works\",\n   \"cls\": \"services_item white-gradient-light flex flex-col backdrop-blur-2xl accordion w-full\"\n  },\n  {\n   \"title\": \"Identity\",\n   \"body\": \"Your look, your legacy. As the first handshake with the world, brand identity defines both perception and memory. We build everything from streamlined starter packages to expansive brand universes: logos, tone of voice, creative direction, and more. RELATED SERVICES Graphic DesignVisual SystemsBrand Guidelines Reach out for examples! Copied! hey@mantis.works hey@mantis.works\",\n   \"cls\": \"services_item white-gradient-light flex flex-col backdrop-blur-2xl accordion w-full\"\n  },\n  {\n   \"title\": \"Content Production\",\n   \"body\": \"From nimble shoots to full-scale productions, we assemble the right team for the job. Whether independent photographers in the field or full studio partnerships, we deliver efficient, high-quality content that leaves a lasting impression. RELATED SERVICES StoryboardsScriptsLocation ScoutingCastingShooting and CapturePost ProductionSocial OptimizationExperiential Content CaptureCGI / Virtual ProductionPost-Launch Content Toolkits Reach out for examples! Copied! hey@mantis.works hey@mantis.works\",\n   \"cls\": \"services_item white-gradient-light flex flex-col backdrop-blur-2xl accordion w-full\"\n  },\n  {\n   \"title\": \"OOH\",\n   \"body\": \"From billboards and subway media to guerrilla projections and digital trucks, we ensure your brand is visible when and where it matters—and remembered long after the placement comes down. RELATED SERVICES Campaign Planning/StrategyPlacement BuysContent DesignFormat Optimization & DeliveryPrint Management Reach out for examples! Copied! hey@mantis.works hey@mantis.works\",\n   \"cls\": \"services_item white-gradient-light flex flex-col backdrop-blur-2xl accordion w-full\"\n  }\n ],\n \"s3heading\": \"we excite neurons.\",\n \"s3sub\": [\n  \"Experiential\",\n  \"Architecture\",\n  \"Spatial & Interior Design\",\n  \"Interactive / Creative Technology\",\n  \"Event Production\",\n  \"Digital\",\n  \"3D Modelling\",\n  \"Motion & Animation\",\n  \"User Experience / Interface\",\n  \"Development\",\n  \"Brand\",\n  \"Brand & Campaign Strategy\",\n  \"Identity\",\n  \"Content Production\",\n  \"OOH\"\n ],\n \"footerHTMLsample\": \" <div class=\\\"container max-w-none w-full l:px-cont pr-[4.1666666667vw] pl-[20.8333333333vw]\\\"> <div class=\\\"footer_body min-h-screen pt-120 flex flex-col justify-between gap-40 relative z-2 s:gap-30 s:pt-160\\\"> <!-- Titles --> <h3 class=\\\"_72 sm_27 footer_title-parent\\\"> <div class=\\\"flex gap-[0.2em]\\\"> <div class=\\\"footer_title\\\" aria-label=\\\"Let’s build your next\\\"><div aria-hidden=\\\"true\\\" style=\\\"position: relative; display: inline-block; margin-right: -0.1em; padding-right: 0.1em; margin-bottom: -0.1em; padding-bottom: 0.1em; overflow: clip;\\\"><div class=\\\"footer_char\\\" aria-hidden=\\\"true\\\" style=\\\"position: relative; display: inline-block; translate: none; rotate: none; scale: none; transform: translate(0px, 0px);\\\">L</div><div class=\\\"footer_char\\\" aria-hidden=\\\"true\\\" style=\\\"position: relative; display: inline-block; translate: none; rotate: none; scale: none; transform: translate(0px, 0px);\\\">e</div><div class=\\\"footer_char\\\" aria-hidden=\\\"true\\\" style=\\\"position: relative; display: inline-block; translate: none; rotate: none; scale: none; transform: translate(0px, 